channel.title: Looking for opinions
channel.description: Ok.. ive been experimenting with rsps's for the last 3 weeks and i got to a point where i want to start from a clean base. this is what im about to use (:http://www.rune-server.org/runescape-development/rs2-server/downloads/252677-project-insanity-cleaned-version-2-a.html) inless anyone thinks i should use somthing different. i just want a clean base i can start a good server off of..(i have a client but i dont know the details,if anyone has a good client they kno about that could help too.. lol)

item.title: Looking for opinions
item.dc:creator: @strucker Strucker
item.description:
@strucker wrote:

tyb97:

Hyperion/Apollo… Anything that doesn’t load a higher cache than what it should PI loads 474, so I wouldn’t advise using it. RandQm has released a good Delta base, it’s called “Project Zeta”, check it out, also. I would advise learning java first, then coming here and doing some work.

Hyperion might be a little tricky when you’re starting…
but yes, i agree with delta…
